Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.48,0:00:05.50,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Dad? You mean him?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.50,0:00:07.48,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,So he's having an affair?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.45,0:00:10.77,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Break them up? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.77,0:00:14.35,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,You're in junior high, \Nfigure it out, octopus!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.35,0:00:16.09,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You. What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.09,0:00:16.86,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.86,0:00:17.37,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Sayu!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.20,0:00:21.83,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like your dad either.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.14,0:00:24.61,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,He's got a kid and he's trying \Nto get with a younger woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.61,0:00:27.82,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,He's not fit for Akari... \Nmy big sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.82,0:00:31.00,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Your sister's the one\Nwho's tricking him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.48,0:00:32.47,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.66,0:00:39.64,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.18,0:00:42.58,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why you—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.58,0:00:47.03,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like playing \Ndirty like you, Miuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.00,0:00:52.98,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.08,0:00:56.89,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's his problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.89,0:00:58.08,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,He won't get away with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.08,0:01:00.83,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna! Let's fry him up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.83,0:01:02.82,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,We'll make him into takoyaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.32,0:01:05.40,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.05,0:02:42.05,Episode-Title - Copy,episode,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 4: Because We're Friends
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.08,0:02:46.52,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that's amazing, Hii-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:48.34,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,You're really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.34,0:02:50.02,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a big deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.13,0:02:53.68,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Your cheek's twitching.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:02:58.65,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,You're really good too, Tsumugu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.65,0:03:00.54,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,When did you learn how to cook?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.54,0:03:02.07,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.34,0:03:04.50,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,It's always been just\Nme and Gramps, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.50,0:03:07.46,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That's very admirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.39,0:03:11.79,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,W-We don't need that \Nmuch Chinese cabbage...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.41,0:03:19.61,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:24.93,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Let's all go around to \Nthe other groups and try their food.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:26.66,Main,kids,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:26.31,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.66,0:03:27.56,Main,Seiki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, give me some.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.56,0:03:29.31,Main,boy,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? The carrot's so big.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.01,0:03:34.15,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.15,0:03:35.85,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.83,0:03:40.19,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.88,0:03:43.34,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Please... try this if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.34,0:03:44.16,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.16,0:03:45.73,Main,egawa,0000,0000,0000,,"Try this"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.32,0:03:49.84,Main,egawa,0000,0000,0000,,Like there's any way we could eat \Nanything you sea people make.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.84,0:03:50.79,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:52.43,Main,person,0000,0000,0000,,It smells pretty fishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.43,0:03:53.29,Main,egawa,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.29,0:03:56.05,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,B-But... there isn't \Neven any fish in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.05,0:03:57.13,Main,egawa,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want any.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.98,0:04:00.68,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.68,0:04:02.84,Main,egawa,0000,0000,0000,,I said I don't want any!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.47,0:04:09.60,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:10.69,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.24,0:04:14.65,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumugu-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.65,0:04:17.79,Main,egawa,0000,0000,0000,,What for? My hand just \Naccidentally bumped her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.79,0:04:19.32,Main,person,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.32,0:04:20.40,Main,person,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:23.00,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:24.50,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.70,0:04:27.89,Main,both,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.05,0:04:46.93,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to eat your lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.39,0:04:49.40,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,We just ate...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.66,0:04:50.85,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go work on Ojoshi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.85,0:04:52.52,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:10.62,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:13.37,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe we should try harder\Nto get along with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.37,0:05:15.96,Wood Shop Room,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Wood Shop Room
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.37,0:05:15.96,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,With the guys that waste food?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.28,0:05:22.04,Main,hkari,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.04,0:05:22.92,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,This is horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.29,0:05:25.09,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Who would do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.09,0:05:26.61,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,It's them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.23,0:05:30.51,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.51,0:05:32.82,Main,egawa,0000,0000,0000,,Half arm suplex!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.82,0:05:34.75,Main,person,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.16,0:05:38.31,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.20,0:05:42.26,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.77,0:05:48.28,Main,princ,0000,0000,0000,,It's wrong that the Ojoshi-sama \Nwas broken, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.28,0:05:50.69,Main,egawa,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.88,0:05:53.29,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Stop lying! Then who the hell did it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.31,0:05:53.71,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop. Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.92,0:05:53.31,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hii-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.79,0:05:56.94,Main,princ,0000,0000,0000,,You're a little too excited today, \Nso this isn't going anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.94,0:05:59.57,Main,princ,0000,0000,0000,,We'll talk about this further tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.57,0:06:00.82,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.82,0:06:03.62,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari, you can go home for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.08,0:06:05.76,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only one you're sending home?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:07.69,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Am I the only bad guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.69,0:06:08.65,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:09.97,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Well, excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.97,0:06:11.54,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.29,0:06:13.50,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going home, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.50,0:06:14.39,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,You, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:16.50,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, but you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:18.49,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,You still have fourth period...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.49,0:06:20.23,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go home, so I'm going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:21.89,Main,teach,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.40,0:06:29.79,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka is really stubborn \Nwhen she gets like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.08,0:06:32.77,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't coming off very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:35.54,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:38.99,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,She's a scaredy cat, but \Nhas a strong will...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.99,0:06:42.00,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,a gorgeous body... big, round eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:44.50,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,and she's always trying so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:46.55,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,And you're big.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.30,0:06:49.71,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,You're too blunt, Kaname.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.71,0:06:52.01,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,There are guys who prefer bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.28,0:06:53.80,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.80,0:06:57.31,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently middle-aged men prefer \Nit when girls aren't so skinny.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:06:58.72,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.12,0:07:01.02,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Following with that doesn't help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.61,0:07:03.52,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,You should just be honest and be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.03,0:07:05.61,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.41,0:07:09.90,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I really should be more \Nhonest like Manaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.66,0:07:17.79,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,"Sayu has arrived"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.79,0:07:18.80,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Sayu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.07,0:07:20.13,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.13,0:07:21.24,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.24,0:07:24.67,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,She's one of the mysterious grade \Nschool kids that has a grudge against Hikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.67,0:07:26.00,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Grade school kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.41,0:07:29.00,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,That's a rather blunt \Ncriminal declaration.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.38,0:07:31.32,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,So it wasn't the guys from our class.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.71,0:07:34.55,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Chisaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.93,0:07:36.91,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep this a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.91,0:07:38.93,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep this between us, Kaname.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.93,0:07:40.93,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.93,0:07:44.00,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Because if everyone else\Nfinds out about this,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:45.85,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari will end up the bad guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.27,0:07:46.92,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.92,0:07:50.94,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I can't watch Hikari\Nbeing hurt any further.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.94,0:07:54.32,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Bad guy or not, it's true that \Nit was a misunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.95,0:07:58.17,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a good thing to lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.73,0:08:00.26,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,It'll just isolate you even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.26,0:08:01.21,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.21,0:08:05.78,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,They're people who were saying \Nthat our food smelled fishy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.78,0:08:08.17,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,They're really not bad people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:11.44,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,The people who purposely \Nspilled the sushi bowl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:15.76,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were a good person,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.76,0:08:19.01,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,but I guess you're a person\N from the surface after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.41,0:08:27.03,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take it personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:31.64,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Chisaki loses her head when \Nit comes to Hikari or Manaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.64,0:08:32.69,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.69,0:08:37.05,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I love the ocean, and \Nthe people of Shishio.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:40.64,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,So I don't want everyone \Nto misunderstand Hikari
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.64,0:08:42.82,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,just because he\Nmisunderstands all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.25,0:08:47.00,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, could you say\Nthat one more time?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.74,0:08:50.04,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want everyone \Nto misunderstand Hikari
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.04,0:08:52.38,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,just because he\Nmisunderstands all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.38,0:08:55.38,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, got it.
