Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.61,0:09:08.65,Flashback,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,561)}I don't like playing \Ndirty like you, Miuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.47,0:09:13.15,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.17,0:09:15.26,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.26,0:09:16.61,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I gave it to 'em good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.61,0:09:17.11,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.11,0:09:19.95,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,You know they were making \Nan Ojoshi-sama, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:21.58,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I totally ruined it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.49,0:09:23.95,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Ruined?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:24.41,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:26.09,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I drew all over it
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.09,0:09:30.28,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,and ripped the clothes so that you\Ncan't even tell it's Ojoshi-sama anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:31.49,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,For real!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.49,0:09:33.30,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you do that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:34.38,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.38,0:09:36.26,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,That's really playing dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:38.18,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,M-Miuna?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.18,0:09:42.64,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I... I hate playing dirty like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:44.17,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.56,0:09:49.39,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hii-kun, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:51.57,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you follow me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:55.53,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:57.22,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,An octopus...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.71,0:09:59.99,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Here, boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.18,0:10:02.87,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Octopuses are cowards.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.19,0:10:07.21,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,You know, you're probably \N like an octopus.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.21,0:10:09.52,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to call \Nme an octopus, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.52,0:10:11.26,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? "Too"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.26,0:10:12.79,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.79,0:10:16.86,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,When they get scared by fish\Nthey don't know, they spit out ink.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.86,0:10:18.18,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Like dark black stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:21.31,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,But the ink is really \Ngood if you eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.31,0:10:22.94,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Squid ink pasta, for example.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.94,0:10:25.01,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Or would it be octopus ink?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.01,0:10:26.60,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I've never made that so...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.60,0:10:28.00,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:29.94,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What was it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:37.53,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why'd you bring them\Nthe sushi bowl in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.53,0:10:38.62,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.62,0:10:40.83,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't usually \Ndo something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.13,0:10:43.09,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You're usually hiding behind us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.39,0:10:44.98,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.24,0:10:47.61,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Another octopus?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.61,0:10:49.33,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,No... Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.54,0:10:56.31,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,That's... Akari's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.66,0:11:10.91,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hii-kun, the bottom's turning black!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.91,0:11:11.94,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.51,0:11:15.41,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You can't even make rice \Nporridge by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.46,0:11:19.52,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we can just put in \Nsome miso and cover it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.52,0:11:20.75,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.13,0:11:23.16,Main,person,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.73,0:11:25.53,Main,person,0000,0000,0000,,I've caused you some trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.53,0:11:26.76,Main,person,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.76,0:11:29.65,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You have something else to \Napologize for, you criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.65,0:11:31.38,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,C-Criminal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.38,0:11:34.46,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You have a kid and yet you're\Ntrying to get with my big sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:35.54,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:38.73,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,The hell were you drowning for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.09,0:11:41.68,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been able to contact Akari.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.68,0:11:43.78,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,She won't come to the supermarket,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.44,0:11:47.52,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,so I thought I'd come \Nsee her directly myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.52,0:11:50.18,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Directly? You mean to Shioshishio?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.18,0:11:51.09,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.63,0:11:54.44,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,I borrowed some diving \Nequipment from my friend,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.44,0:11:56.92,Main,dad,0000,0000,0000,,but it kept filling up with water...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.13,0:11:59.44,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you get off\N playing the sad victim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:01.28,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't, Hii-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:04.28,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You're a criminal. A perpetrator!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:07.20,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Affairs are totally unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.18,0:12:16.66,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Uroko-sama, could you \Nspare some sacred fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.96,0:12:26.14,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite the sinner, \Nwalking over the servant of a god.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.14,0:12:27.31,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.31,0:12:29.95,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Despite how much I've cleaned up around here,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.95,0:12:32.05,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,and despite all the things I've done for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.59,0:12:34.69,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I still ended up having a terrible time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.69,0:12:37.47,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,How long do you plan not to go to work?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.47,0:12:39.85,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking about \Nfinding a job around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.36,0:12:42.50,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Though there's not much around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.50,0:12:46.19,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to give up on him \Nbecause his daughter didn't approve?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.76,0:12:50.95,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,You seem to know a lot of gossip \Ndespite being cooped up in here all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.29,0:12:57.47,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,It's only been three years \Nsince she lost her mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.82,0:13:00.34,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand why she \Ncan't approve of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.96,0:13:05.19,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,The girl's mother was Miori, who \Nlived in a house just off the rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.19,0:13:06.73,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,So you remember her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.73,0:13:08.09,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.09,0:13:10.72,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,She was a real beauty\Nwith an enormous ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.89,0:13:17.64,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Despite Miori-san being from here, \Nthey treated me really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.98,0:13:20.23,Cafe Triangle,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Café Triangle
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.18,0:13:25.95,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna-chan is actually really cute...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:28.52,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,like a little baby sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:34.18,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,And with Itaru-san, they were
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.18,0:13:35.66,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,the family that I had admired.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:38.12,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone was always smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.28,0:13:45.63,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.73,0:13:48.68,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Miori-san's funeral...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.73,0:13:51.14,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Miuna-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:52.42,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,was bawling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.84,0:13:55.28,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,It was the first time I ever \Nsaw her cry like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.63,0:13:58.19,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,and it reminded me of Hikari\Nwhen he was younger, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.93,0:13:59.95,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.67,0:14:04.23,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.23,0:14:08.25,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to stay by them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.48,0:14:11.74,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I could fill the hole \Nthat Miori-san left behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.74,0:14:13.54,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,It's all about how you say things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.54,0:14:14.35,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.35,0:14:16.21,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,That's just illicit love.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.21,0:14:20.28,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Miori was gone and you \Nwanted to steal her place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.69,0:14:25.26,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,That's harsh, Uroko-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.13,0:14:31.36,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't mind putting a curse on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.36,0:14:32.26,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,A curse?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.73,0:14:35.47,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,A curse to make you forget \Nthe man you fell for.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.99,0:14:40.56,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.73,0:14:43.77,Main,akari,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of this on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.91,0:14:49.49,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,Akari is still such a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:53.24,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,There's only so much \Nyou can do on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:59.21,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,I know, Lord Sea God.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.00,0:15:04.96,Main,uroko,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let the surface have \Nthe people of the sea right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.94,0:15:20.01,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Ojoshi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.01,0:15:20.89,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.61,0:15:22.92,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.92,0:15:23.86,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.86,0:15:25.73,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who ruined it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.58,0:15:30.76,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.51,0:15:36.00,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you get mad at her, Hii-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.00,0:15:38.83,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's not like I don't \Nknow how she feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.83,0:15:39.70,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:43.62,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,After my mom died, if some \Nother woman came into my house,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.62,0:15:45.54,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I probably wouldn't \Nhave liked it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.52,0:15:54.17,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Wh— Why are you crying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.17,0:15:56.36,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Uroko-sama told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.36,0:15:59.70,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,that I'm always being protected
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.19,0:16:02.81,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,by you and Chii-chan and Kaname...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.81,0:16:04.43,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Uroko-sama did?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.43,0:16:06.51,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,And I think that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.51,0:16:09.05,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Uroko-sama says something \Ngood once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.57,0:16:11.42,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,You're nice, Hii-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.42,0:16:13.14,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.36,0:16:15.48,Main,mana,0000,0000,0000,,You can protect others...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.50,0:16:21.32,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, let's go apologize \Nto everyone together!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.32,0:16:23.33,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.50,0:16:26.54,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Even though they're gonna \Nhave a lot to say in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.54,0:16:28.73,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,And they'll say a lot to me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.73,0:16:29.55,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:33.30,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I want to protect you \Nfrom now on, Hii-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.12,0:16:35.56,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to protect you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.01,0:16:38.43,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.33,0:16:44.51,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.76,0:16:47.65,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.05,0:16:52.12,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.69,0:16:57.11,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I was supposed to be the \None to protect Manaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.61,0:17:05.30,Italics,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,But instead, Manaka protected \Nme as if she were Ena.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.86,0:17:25.79,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.26,0:17:28.44,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a sec?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.12,0:17:31.36,Main,egawa,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.86,0:17:34.94,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.22,0:17:38.53,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.53,0:17:41.67,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.67,0:17:42.74,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.74,0:17:46.90,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I'm sorry for thinking it \Nwas you that destroyed Ojoshi-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.90,0:17:49.52,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop, Hikari...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.32,0:17:49.56,Main,kids,0000,0000,0000,,Dude, he's totally on his knees.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.56,0:17:50.67,Main,kids,0000,0000,0000,,I never saw anyone do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.67,0:17:51.54,Main,chisa,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.54,0:17:53.12,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.36,0:17:53.96,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.96,0:17:56.41,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hii-kun feels really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.41,0:17:59.30,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive him. Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.20,0:18:01.30,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Manaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.30,0:18:03.51,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive them, already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.51,0:18:04.81,Main,egawa,0000,0000,0000,,Tsumugu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.81,0:18:08.08,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,You guys were responsible \Nfor the sushi bowl, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.44,0:18:09.48,Main,tsumu,0000,0000,0000,,You're both equally responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:11.09,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,We're not equal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.09,0:18:13.55,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You guys threw around \Nthe sushi bowl...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.80,0:18:19.08,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,But I blamed you guys, \Nand then chested you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.08,0:18:19.91,Main,egawa,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.91,0:18:21.55,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.55,0:18:24.08,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,and come at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.99,0:18:26.50,Main,manaka,0000,0000,0000,,Hii-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:27.41,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.59,0:18:33.25,Main,egawa,0000,0000,0000,,Chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.37,0:18:39.43,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,D-Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.33,0:18:45.61,Main,egawa,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough. This is annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.61,0:18:46.84,Main,egawa,0000,0000,0000,,I forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.93,0:19:17.38,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,When do you actually go to school?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.06,0:19:19.55,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:23.70,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty much the one responsible\Nfor Hikari apologizing on his knees like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:27.56,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Hikari is my very dear friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.90,0:19:31.68,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,And as his friend, I won't forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.74,0:19:44.48,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm... I'm Miuna's friend too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.48,0:19:45.04,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.04,0:19:49.00,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,She's my... she's my \Nreally good, dear friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:51.53,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,When I was in second grade,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.38,0:19:55.00,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,everyone picked on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.53,0:19:59.71,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,But Miuna didn't pick on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:03.68,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Then, people were picking on Miuna...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.68,0:20:06.79,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,And I was sort of relieved...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.79,0:20:10.14,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,that it wasn't me getting picked on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.62,0:20:12.56,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,But Miuna...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:14.48,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much they ignored her...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.48,0:20:16.35,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,She was totally fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.73,0:20:17.62,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.09,0:20:22.11,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.90,0:20:25.05,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you okay with getting picked on...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.37,0:20:27.49,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,and people not liking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.58,0:20:31.20,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Because it doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.68,0:20:35.46,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,Because they're people I don't care about,\Nthat have nothing to do with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.46,0:20:38.32,Main,miuna,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't care what they think of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.56,0:20:44.09,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,That's when...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.09,0:20:47.64,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I don't care what \Npeople think about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.87,0:20:50.22,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if people hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.22,0:20:54.10,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to be dear to Miuna.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.79,0:20:59.07,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Can you apologize to Hikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.07,0:21:00.33,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.85,0:21:04.15,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Since you understand how dear someone \Ncan be to you, you can, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.35,0:21:07.37,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
