Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.85,0:21:20.89,Main,sayu,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-I... I'm really sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.44,0:21:23.80,Main,kaname,0000,0000,0000,,And so, please forgive her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.26,0:21:25.36,Main,hikari,0000,0000,0000,,You did...
